      <title>特朗普的关税威胁扰乱全球市场，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普重申计划自周六起对加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，尽管原油贸易可能不受征税影响，油价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 23:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨，股指期货因盈利而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司和英特尔公司强劲的盈利提振了市场人气，美国和欧洲股指期货上涨，同时由于交易员为特朗普总统周六宣布的关税做好准备，美元也上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 22:37:00 GMT</pubDate>
